&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;full-at&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;98&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;format-charging&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;label-charging&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;format-discharging&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;label-discharging&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;format-full&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;lt;label-full&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;label-charging&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; %percentage%%&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;label-discharging&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; %percentage%%&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;label-full&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; %percentage%%&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/details&gt;
&lt;details&gt;
&lt;summary&gt; powermenu &lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stays inside rofi config, but you can put it anywhere.
Just make sure to provide the correct path&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tmux Plugins</title><link>https://yeasin50.github.io/yt/linux/04_tmux/03_plugins/</link><pubDate>Mon, 05 Jan 2026 20:00:00 +0600</pubDate><guid>https://yeasin50.github.io/yt/linux/04_tmux/03_plugins/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Make it look better and Must have plugins for 10x dev.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;"&gt;
&lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/M7sHtH1tYRE?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check the &lt;a href="https://github.com/yeasin50/.dotfiles"&gt;GitHub Dotfiles&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# .... previouse configs&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @plugin &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;tmux-plugins/tpm&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @plugin &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;tmux-plugins/tmux-sensible&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @plugin &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;tmux-plugins/tmux-resurrect&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @plugin &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;tmux-plugins/tmux-yank&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @plugin &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;dracula/tmux&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt; 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @dracula-show-powerline true
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @dracula-plugins &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;cpu-usage ram-usage&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g @dracula-show-gpu false
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;run &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;~/.tmux/plugins/tpm/tpm&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# your tmp path&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set-option -g base-index &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set-option -g pane-base-index &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;17&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set-option -g set-clipboard on
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;19&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;bind -n M-Left &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;select&lt;/span&gt;-pane -L
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;bind -n M-Right &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;select&lt;/span&gt;-pane -R
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;bind -n M-Up &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;select&lt;/span&gt;-pane -U
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;bind -n M-Down &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;select&lt;/span&gt;-pane -D
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;23&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;24&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;set -g status-position top
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Selection &amp; Copy-Paste in TMUX</title><link>https://yeasin50.github.io/yt/linux/04_tmux/04_copy_paste/</link><pubDate>Wed, 07 Jan 2026 20:00:00 +0600</pubDate><guid>https://yeasin50.github.io/yt/linux/04_tmux/04_copy_paste/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;How can we copy and paste text in TMUX?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;"&gt;
&lt;iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen" loading="eager" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ch9IApO7O1o?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;" title="YouTube video"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check the &lt;a href="https://github.com/yeasin50/.dotfiles"&gt;GitHub Dotfiles&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are using the &lt;strong&gt;tmux-yank&lt;/strong&gt; plugin from the previous video.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To select text:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Press &lt;code&gt;Ctrl + b&lt;/code&gt; to enter TMUX command mode.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move the cursor to the start of the text you want to select.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Press &lt;code&gt;Space&lt;/code&gt; to start the selection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move the cursor to the end of the text.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Press &lt;code&gt;y&lt;/code&gt; to copy the selection to the system clipboard.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Or just drag the mouse to select text and press y to copy&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Git with SSH &amp; Multiple Repo</title><link>https://yeasin50.github.io/yt/git/100_git_ssh_auth/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 13:01:40 +0600</pubDate><guid>https://yeasin50.github.io/yt/git/100_git_ssh_auth/</guid><description>Setup SSH authentication for GitHub and Codeberg, and manage multiple Git remotes from a single local repository.</description></item></channel></rss>